as their mysterious statues.
A welcome return for Dear Diary (Radio 4 at 10.00am). This is a simple idea
 -extracts from diarists of the past writing around this day - which works
wonderfully. We eavesdrop on a peregrination around Birmingham in 1837 and a
doctor in Hiroshima on his earth-shattering day in 1945.
